comments: Sengun (HOU) establishes himself as he firms up in Harden's (LAC) path and absorbs the contact during the screen.
Sengun (HOU) brings both hands to Plumlee's (LAC) chest away from the play in an attempt to commit a take foul in the last two minutes.
Brooks (HOU) slides his hand off Powell's (LAC) side as they come together and separate following the pick.
Brooks (HOU) extends his hands into Leonard's (LAC) arm and body, which affects his SQBR and ability to pass.
Green's (HOU) arm is extended when contact occurs with Powell's (LAC) arm during his upward shooting motion.
Harden (LAC) gets his left hand to the ball to dislodge it as his right hand makes marginal contact with VanVleet (HOU).
Harden (LAC) is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds, and the possession is correctly given to HOU.
Harden (LAC) extends his left leg into VanVleet's (HOU) path and initiates contact with VanVleet's lower body, affecting his driving shot attempt.
Leonard (LAC) dislodges Sengun (HOU) during the loose ball.
Brooks (HOU) makes contact with the ball after Plumlee (LAC) gathers the rebound and briefly gets tangled up before Brooks deflects the ball away. Any ensuing contact is deemed incidental.
Sengun (HOU) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Sengun (HOU) lightly brushes George's (LAC) arm, and marginal contact occurs as George secures the rebound.
Sengun (HOU) is trailing when he turns and delivers contact into George's (LAC) body, which affects George's driving shot attempt.
All Technical Fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Harden (LAC) briefly places his hands on Green's (HOU) side during the drive and retracts them before Green loses control of the ball by dribbling it off his leg.
Sengun (HOU) commits a take foul on Harden (LAC).
Sengun (HOU) commits a take foul on Harden (LAC).
Sengun (HOU) brings his off-arm outward, and marginal contact occurs with Leonard (LAC) as he contests the driving shot attempt.
